Class AngleBase3DShapes

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shapes
      • ThreeDimensionalShapes
        • AngleBase3DShapes
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Cube, Octahedron, Pyramid, Tetrahedron

    public class AngleBase3DShapes
extends ThreeDimensionalShapes
    Version:
    1.0

    This is a subclass of ThreeDimensionalShapes. This will contain the 3D shapes that have angles and on rounded sides. All these shapes are Regular 3D shapes.

    Author:
    Alex Wong
